images.prompt: In a hauntingly enchanting landscape drenched in swamp light, a cursed doll with hauntingly exaggerated features hovers amidst a dreamlike aura, its porcelain skin reflecting shades of electric violet and sky cyan, while ethereal string lights flicker around it, casting an otherworldly glow that warps perception through a dynamic zoom blur, blurring the lines between reality and the surreal, evoking a sense of eerie whimsy and unsettling beauty that invites the viewer to explore the depths of an unsettling yet captivating realm.

A towering crystal giantess emerges from the shadowy depths of ancient, torchlit ruins, her body intricately adorned with deep jade hues that refract the flickering light around her, while volcanic gray rock merges seamlessly into her form, revealing her intertwined nature with the earth; as the viewer gazes deeper, a mesmerizing vortex eye draws them into the swirling energies of her being, where strands of bleeding circuits pulse rhythmically beneath her crystalline skin, casting an otherworldly glow that accentuates the surreal landscape of her domain, imbued with the essence of new wave aesthetics that blend modernity and mysticism into a captivating, dynamic interplay of colors and shapes that evoke both awe and a sense of haunting beauty within this fantastical world.
